OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1775671869
OL,3,CTeenager who threatened to kill
OL,4,Cchicken shop worker over garlic sauce
OL,5,Cis jailed
OL,7,FA man who pulled out a fake gun and
OL,8,Fthreatened to kill a chicken shop
OL,9,Fworker on Christmas Eve after
OL,10,Fcomplaining about not receiving garlic
OL,11,Fsauce has been jailed.
OL,13,FMarwan Khadir, 18, carried out the
OL,14,Farmed attack which lasted more than
OL,15,Ftwo minutes using a realistic
OL,16,Fimitation firearm on December 24 at
OL,17,Fthe shop in south London.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
