OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1775671869
OL,3,CTeenager who threatened to kill
OL,4,Cchicken shop worker over garlic sauce
OL,5,Cis jailed
OL,7,FHe threatened to shoot and kill the
OL,8,Fworker and assaulted him multiple
OL,9,Ftimes after complaining about his
OL,10,Forder.
OL,12,FKhadir, of Malcolm Close, Penge, was
OL,13,Fsentenced to three years' imprisonment
OL,14,Fat Woolwich Crown Court on Tuesday,
OL,15,Fpolice said.
OL,17,FA video released by police of the
OL,18,Fincident shows Khadir asking the
OL,19,Femployee "how many garlic sauces did
OL,20,Fyou put in the bag?", adding: "I asked
OL,21,Fyou for chips."
OL,26,@{D@JOU|D@TO]|D@_OU}D@OO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
