OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1775671869
OL,3,CTeenager who threatened to kill
OL,4,Cchicken shop worker over garlic sauce
OL,5,Cis jailed
OL,7,FKhadir then returned to his home and
OL,8,Fdiscovered wrong sauces in the bag,
OL,9,Fwith video showing him pacing around
OL,10,Fhis flat and gesticulating while
OL,11,Fcomplaining about the order on the
OL,12,Fphone.
OL,14,FHe then returns to the shop and shouts
OL,15,Fat the employee: "Bossman, come here.
OL,17,F"Why you give me four burger sauce? I
OL,18,Fasked for three garlic and three mayo."
OL,26,@wD@ROUyD@AOUzD@gO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
