OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1775671869
OL,3,CTeenager who threatened to kill
OL,4,Cchicken shop worker over garlic sauce
OL,5,Cis jailed
OL,7,FHe then asks the worker to open the
OL,8,Fdoor of the counter and jumps on it
OL,9,Fbefore being pushed back.
OL,11,FKhadir then pulls out the imitation
OL,12,Ffirearm, cocks it, and shouts: "I'm
OL,13,Fgoing to kill you now, are you mad?"
OL,15,FOfficers identified Khadir through
OL,16,FCCTV and financial tracking, as well
OL,17,Fas local resident checks between
OL,18,FChristmas and New Years' Day, police
OL,19,Fsaid.
OL,26,@tD@`OUuD@dO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1775671869
OL,3,CTeenager who threatened to kill
OL,4,Cchicken shop worker over garlic sauce
OL,5,Cis jailed
OL,7,FHe was arrested on January 2 by armed
OL,8,Fpolice and officers seized the replica
OL,9,Fgun he used in the attack, as well as
OL,10,Ffake ammunition.
OL,12,FDetective Sergeant Amy Cross, who led
OL,13,Fthe investigation, said: "The tireless
OL,14,Fwork by officers on this case over the
OL,15,FChristmas and new year period is
OL,16,Ffurther evidence that policing never
OL,17,Fstops, and their efforts ultimately
OL,18,Fled to a conviction.
OL,26,@uD@ZOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1775671869
OL,3,CTeenager who threatened to kill
OL,4,Cchicken shop worker over garlic sauce
OL,5,Cis jailed
OL,7,F"All our thoughts continue to remain
OL,8,Fwith the victim of this terrifying
OL,9,Fordeal, something no one should ever
OL,10,Fhave to go through, let alone at their
OL,11,Fplace of work. The strength he has
OL,12,Fshown since the attack has been
OL,13,Fremarkable.
OL,15,F"On top of this, the courage he
OL,16,Fdemonstrated in coming forward and
OL,17,Freporting the assault was incredibly
OL,18,Fbrave. He was then able to
OL,19,Fsubsequently identify the perpetrator,
OL,20,Fa crucial moment in allowing us to
OL,21,Fmove the investigation forward."
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOU}D@`O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/8
