CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1775671869
OL,3,CTeenager who threatened to kill
OL,4,Cchicken shop worker over garlic sauce
OL,5,Cis jailed
OL,7,FKhadir pleaded guilty at Woolwich
OL,8,FCrown Court on January 30 to
OL,9,Fpossessing an imitation firearm with
OL,10,Fintent to cause fear of violence,
OL,11,Fmaking threats to kill and assault
OL,12,Foccasioning actual bodily harm.
